{"word":"Walking with God","slug":"walking-with-god","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Walking with God</b> According to His commands<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=33'>Deu 5:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=1&verse=6'>Psa 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=23'>Jer 7:23</a><br/> In His ways<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=28&verse=9'>Deu 28:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=22&verse=5'>Jos 22:5</a><br/> In the old paths<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=16'>Jer 6:16</a><br/> As taught by Him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=36'>1Ki 8:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=3'>Isa 2:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=21'>Isa 30:21</a><br/> Uprightly<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=2&verse=7'>Pro 2:7</a><br/> In His statutes and judgments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=37&verse=24'>Eze 37:24</a><br/> In newness of life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=6&verse=4'>Rom 6:4</a><br/> Not after the flesh, but after the Spirit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=1'>Rom 8:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=16'>Gal 5:16</a><br/> Honestly, as in the day<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=13&verse=13'>Rom 13:13</a><br/> by faith, not by sight<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=5&verse=7'>2Co 5:7</a><br/> In love, following Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=2'>Eph 5:2</a><br/> Worthy of the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=1&verse=10'>Col 1:1